task.summary:
First fully workable build. Were added XML file parser (class Parser), driver class that launches tests (uses testNG framework). And more useful classes that were deployed during the creation of this project.
Need to do next: reformat, write comments and maybe some things more.
14.11.19

Release 1.0
First fully workable build reformatted.
Were added different type of comments and removed unused stuff.
14.11.19

Release 1.1
Minor fixes in class DerpyTester
14.11.19

Refactored according to supervisor's advice. Now all Action classes have their own package (actions). All Action subclasses now implement functional interface IAction with method run(). Reorganized Action subclasses objects parsing and their execution.
Killer feature: if program receives via XML file test scenarios that include actions that are not defined then they could be treated as "unsupported yet action".
And few more more minor improvements are added.
Further steps: refactoring.
27.11.19

Refactored classes in package "actions". Added class "SimpleLogger" that writes logs if 'Unrecognizable' action gets processed.
Refactored POM.xml file. Unused dependencies deleted and changed groupID and artifactId tags.
+ few more improvements
Further steps: refactoring.
28.11.19 - 29.11.19

Refactored classes in package "actions". Added class "SimpleLogger" that writes logs if 'Unrecognizable' action gets processed. Added logs folder that represents example of a log file.
Added action class "MaximizeWindowAct" that maximizes window of a browser.
Refactored POM.xml file. Unused dependencies deleted and changed groupID and artifactId tags.
+ few more improvements
Further steps: refactoring.
28.11.19 - 29.11.19

Added instance of up-to date log file.
Further steps: refactoring.
29.11.19

Added support of an enterprise - grade report tool. Now program generates representative and comprehendable reports. Added one more action and refactored class Parser.
+ more minor improvements
